    Verse: 2
Tags:
  - Principle
---
This is an eternal and fundamental principle, inherent in all things, in
every system of philosophy, in every religion and in every science. There is
no getting away from the law of love. It is feeling that imparts vitality
to thought. Feeling is desire, and desire is love. Thought impregnated
with love becomes invincible.
